      <title>Transit</title>
      <link>http://dev.bluevisual.tv/personal/transit/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Mar 2016 10:36:54 -0400</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://dev.bluevisual.tv/personal/transit/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Transit (as it&amp;rsquo;s currently called) is a project that&amp;rsquo;s been conceptual for a few years now but is finally coming to fruition now that VR is an available medium (and a perfect one at that!). It&amp;rsquo;s a project about experiencing beautiful places and things.

&lt;div style=&#34;position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; padding-top: 30px; height: 0; overflow: hidden;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;iframe src=&#34;//player.vimeo.com/video/171832381&#34; style=&#34;position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;&#34; webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;Here&amp;#39;s a preview video of it playing inside Unreal Engine&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You are in a cabin gliding along rails through beautiful environments and places. There are hardly any controls, only some gaze-activated menus inside your cabin. This is to let the player not worry about navigating environments, getting stuck somewhere, or needing to interact with anything in the real world.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;project-image&#34; oncontextmenu=&#34;return false;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle1&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://dev.bluevisual.tv/images/personal/transit-01.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/label&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;A view from the level &amp;#39;Terminal&amp;#39;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;input type=&#34;checkbox&#34; name=&#34;lightbox-toggle1&#34; id=&#34;lightbox-toggle1&#34; /&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;lightbox&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle1&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://dev.bluevisual.tv/images/personal/transit-01.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;A view from the level &amp;#39;Terminal&amp;#39;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;project-image&#34; oncontextmenu=&#34;return false;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle2&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://dev.bluevisual.tv/images/personal/transit-02.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/label&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;Another view from further back&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;input type=&#34;checkbox&#34; name=&#34;lightbox-toggle2&#34; id=&#34;lightbox-toggle2&#34; /&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;lightbox&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle2&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://dev.bluevisual.tv/images/personal/transit-02.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;Another view from further back&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There will be playlist functionality where you can load up a few different environments in sequence and they will load fairly seamlessly. There will also be looping environments where there is no entrance or exit, only a continuous circuit that you can ride forever. There will also be procedural tracks that go on forever and self-generate, giving you an infinite experience.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;project-image&#34; oncontextmenu=&#34;return false;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle3&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://dev.bluevisual.tv/images/personal/transit-03.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/label&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;Looking forward in &amp;#39;Terminal&amp;#39;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;input type=&#34;checkbox&#34; name=&#34;lightbox-toggle3&#34; id=&#34;lightbox-toggle3&#34; /&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;lightbox&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle3&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://dev.bluevisual.tv/images/personal/transit-03.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;Looking forward in &amp;#39;Terminal&amp;#39;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;project-image&#34; oncontextmenu=&#34;return false;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle4&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://dev.bluevisual.tv/images/personal/transit-04.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/label&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;The transition tunnel that connects each level&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;input type=&#34;checkbox&#34; name=&#34;lightbox-toggle4&#34; id=&#34;lightbox-toggle4&#34; /&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;lightbox&#34;&gt;
  &lt;label for=&#34;lightbox-toggle4&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://dev.bluevisual.tv/images/personal/transit-04.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;caption&#34;&gt;The transition tunnel that connects each level&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There is no objective to this game besides relaxing and enjoying the worlds you&amp;rsquo;re in, escaping to great places you could never go in real life.&lt;/p&gt;

